<p>
	A lovely fresh oil for burning which is made with essential oils reputed to be great for asthma sufferers. Each bottle contains a dropper so the oil does not pour out quickly. This oil has a lovely and fresh aroma, providing a clear easy-breathe atmosphere in any room. It is made with essential oils reputed to help breathing and therefore is designed specifically for asthma sufferers.</p>
<p>
	Directions: put five drops into a burner and place in room for relaxing relief, alternatively at night or for children, place five drops onto a damp clean cloth and then drape the cloth on a radiator in a room or bedroom at night. The heat from the radiator acts as a candle would, vaporising the oil into the room but without the worry of a burning candle or water level in a burner.</p>
<p>
	Ingredients - bergamot essential oil (Citrus bergamia), geranium essential oil (Pelargonium graveolens), lemon essential oil (Citrus limonum), clary sage essential oil (Salvia sclarea) and basil essential oil (Ocimum basilicum). &copy; Please do not copy text- Abluo product description- AVOIL31.&nbsp;</p>
